  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\nI'm currently migrating a large existing application to Quarkus and I want to use [Quarkus Hibernate ORM](https://quarkus.io/guides/hibernate-orm). My existing code is relying on the fact that the entity manager is using the EXTENDED persistence context type, however, quarkus-hibernate-orm seems to be always using PersistenceContextType.TRANSACTION and there is no way of configuring this. Thus, if I wanted to switch now, I would need to refactor a very large portion of the code.\r\n\r\n### Implementation ideas\r\n\r\n_No response_",
